-- Copper Futures Decline 0.2% on Comex in New York, Erase Earlier Gain of 1%
-- Steve Stroth
-- 2010-09-20T12:58:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/copper-futures-decline-0-2-on-comex-in-new-york-erase-earlier-gain-of-1-.html

          
          
             Copper futures for December
delivery fell 1.2 cents, or 0.3 percent, to $3.51 a pound at
8:58 a.m. on the Comex in New York, after earlier gaining as
much as 1 percent.  
          
          


  


        